'''''Internationalist''''' is the third album released by [[Australian]] band [[Powderfinger]] released in [[1998]]. Widely considered as their breakthrough album, ''Internationalist'' earned Powderfinger their first #1 album, as well as widespread critical acclaim and four [[ARIA Awards]], including Best Rock Album and Album Of The Year. 

