==P2K Bonus Disc==
Early pressings of the album included a bonus disc featuring a live recording of Powderfinger's support slot at the [[Crowded_House#Farewell_To_The_World_.282006.29|Crowded House farewell concert]] on the steps of the [[Sydney Opera House]].

