*1999 [[ARIA Awards]], Single Of The Year for ''[[Internationalist (album)|The Day You Come]]'' 
*1999 [[ARIA Awards]], Best Rock Album for ''[[Internationalist (album)|Internationalist]]'' 
*1999 [[ARIA Awards]], Best Cover Art for ''[[Internationalist (album)|Internationalist]]'' 

